<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Employers shall keep a list of workers exposed to group 3 and/or group 4 biological agents, indicating the type of work done and, whenever possible, the biological agent to which they have been exposed, as well as records of exposures, accidents and incidents, as appropriate. </inglise>
