<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> The doctor referred to in Article 14 and/or the competent authority for health and safety at work, and any other person responsible for health and safety at work, shall have access to the list referred to in paragraph 1. </inglise>
